				</div>
				<div class="ingredients">
					<h3>[양념]</h3>
					<hr>
					<span>다진 마늘 1T</span> <span>진간장 2T</span> <span>물 2컵(종이컵)</span> <span>소금
						약간</span> <span>참기름 1T</span>
				</div>
		
			<div class="ingredients">
				<h3>[전분물]</h3>
				<hr>
				<span>전분가루 2T</span> <span>물 4T</span>
			</div>

